  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "This is a feature request for new static analysis module.\r\n\r\n**Issue:** variables that do not change their values should be marked with a keyword \"constant\". Reading from a const variable doesn't cost any gas, it would improve the readability of the code and make it follow the best practices.\r\n\r\n**Recognition:** maybe could be recognised by making use of isAssignment() or isEffect() functions in staticAnalysisCommon module?\r\n\r\n**More:** https://media.readthedocs.org/pdf/solidity/develop/solidity.pdf (Section: \"Constant State Variables\").",
